{
  "texts": [
    "Smoking can cause lung cells to mutate.",
    "Lung-threatening development [31] was the second-leading death cause in 2015, and it is now the fifth scenario in 2017, as determined by the World Health Organization (WHO) evaluation.In comparison to the trained radiologists, the latest cyber-physical technologies and computer-aided detection with Deep Learning has shown promising results in lung cancer diagnosis [127,126,32].",
    "Many different types of Deep Learning [102] architectures have been studied to understand better how to diagnose lung illness.",
    "In [102], a 3D multipath VGG-like system with two setups is suggested.The two groups are kind knobs and dangerous knobs, and lung knobs and non-knobs, respectively.",
    "So various architectural designs are suggested and evaluated in various studies."
  ]
}